<h1>Hamptons Calgary Real Estate and Homes for Sale</h1>
<p>Hamptons has the exclusive air of a quality golf community and the friendly atmosphere prevalent in NW Calgary communities. While soothing views of the greens remind you that the community is special, the neighbourhood events and shared community assets encourage you to engage in civic life.</p>

<div>#idx-c-hamptons#</div>

