        <div class="grid_12">
            <div class="x6">
                <p>Hamptons is a prestigious golf community in NW Calgary. It is built around the members' only Hampton Golf Club, which has hosted Champions League qualifying events, PGA legends exhibitions and local amateur and professional tournaments. Residents enjoy scenic views of fairways, and the opportunity to tee off at the world-class golf course.</p>
                <p>Hamptons is an exclusive community of townhomes and villas. Tirion Properties developed the area in the 1990s. In 2018, the Hamptons Golf Club was redesigned to make room for additional custom-built homes from Shane Homes.</p>
                <p>Neighbourhood amenities include an Olympic size hockey rink, ball diamonds, tennis courts and bike pathways that are connected to Nose Hill Park, a 12-hectare natural environment park. The Belvedere Parkway School serves elementary and kindergarten levels, and there are several schools some distance away from the neighbourhood.</p>
            </div>
